Detailed Description

A graph view made over sets modeling an adjacency matrix.

This Graph view is made of:

  • One SetVar which stores the Set of nodes.
  • One SetVarArray which stores the nodes OutNeighbours. e.g: outN[1] stands for the SetVar which refers to the Set of outNeighbours for Node 1. each line of the matrix is a set variable.
